signatureAbility.signatureDescription: Some running backs have the talent to be elite receivers. When they enter the zone, this ability increases their success rate on possession and RAC catches against single coverage.
When lined up in the backfield, players with this ability have access to four additional hot routes, better route running, and improved catching against linebackers and linemen.
Ballcarriers with this ability have faster spin animations.
Shutdown defenders have the talent to erase receivers from the game. When they enter the zone, their coverage is tighter and interceptions are more frequent on contested catches.
Defenders with this ability will dive for increased range on pass breakups and interceptions.
Players with this ability have an increased chance to catch passes that have been tipped into the air.
When Selfless players are making plays their teammates are motivated to perform better. When they enter the zone, all on field teammates enter the zone as well.
Defenders with this ability can reach out of engaged blocks to tackle or sack nearby ballcarriers.
Defenders with this ability play tighter coverage and force more catch knockouts in both man-to-man and zone.
